@node playin
@prev playin
@next playin

Plays the sample selected in the Input@{u}f@{uu}ile Stringgadget.
@endnode

@node playout
@prev playout
@next playout

Plays the sample selected in the @{u}O@{uu}utputfile Stringgadget.
@endnode

@node convert
@prev convert
@next convert

Starts Sox to convert the file selected in the Input@{u}f@{uu}ile Stringgadget.
@endnode

@node filerequester
@prev filerequester
@next filerequester

Opens an asl-filerequester to select a file.

@endnode

@node dirrequester
@prev dirrequester
@next dirrequester

Opens an asl-filerequester to select a directory.

@endnode

@node checkbox
@prev checkbox
@next checkbox

Please read Sox.guide.

@endnode

@node slider
@prev slider
@next slider

Please read Sox.guide.

@endnode

@node filetyp
@prev filetyp
@next filetyp

Opens an window with all filetypes supported by Sox. The selected filetyp
will be added to the filename in the @{u}O@{uu}utputfile Stringgadget.

@endnode

